OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777227067
OL,3,CImpact of Iran war to last 'up to 12
OL,4,Cmonths' after conflict ends, minister
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe economic impact of the war in Iran
OL,8,Fcould last for eight to 12 months
OL,9,Fafter the conflict is resolved,
OL,10,Faccording to a government minister.
OL,12,FChief secretary to the prime minister
OL,13,FDarren Jones said the main impact of
OL,14,Fthe war would be on the price of
OL,15,Fenergy, food and holidays.
OL,17,FAlready, that is being seen in the
OL,18,Fdata with inflation rising to 3.3% in
OL,19,Fthe year to March.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777227067
OL,3,CImpact of Iran war to last 'up to 12
OL,4,Cmonths' after conflict ends, minister
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FAccording to the RAC, average diesel
OL,8,Fprices have risen by 47.4p and petrol
OL,9,Fprices by 24.5p since the outbreak of
OL,10,Fthe conflict.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FBut Jones, who will chair a new
OL,18,Fcontingency planning group that meets
OL,19,Ftwice a week, said the country will
OL,20,F"start to see food and holiday prices
OL,21,Frise as well".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777227067
OL,3,CImpact of Iran war to last 'up to 12
OL,4,Cmonths' after conflict ends, minister
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FHe added that supply was not the issue
OL,8,Ffor the UK and that "we have robust
OL,9,Fsupply chains and storage in the UK,
OL,10,Fthe main impact is price".
OL,12,FOn Tuesday, the prime minister will
OL,13,Fchair the next meeting of the Middle
OL,14,FEast Response Committee, with the
OL,15,Fgovernment hoping to limit the war's
OL,16,Feffects on the UK.
OL,18,FBut Jones admitted on Sunday that even
OL,19,Fwhen the conflict is resolved, the
OL,20,F"economic scarring" could continue for
OL,21,Fup to a year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777227067
OL,3,CImpact of Iran war to last 'up to 12
OL,4,Cmonths' after conflict ends, minister
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"There will be a delay in energy
OL,8,Fsupplies coming back online after the
OL,9,FStrait of Hormuz is unblocked," he
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FThe Strait of Hormuz has been at the
OL,13,Fcentre of ongoing talks between the
OL,14,FUS, Israel and Iran as global
OL,15,Fshipments of oil, liquefied natural
OL,16,Fgas, fertiliser and other supplies
OL,17,Fhave been heavily disrupted as a
OL,18,Fresult of the conflict, driving up
OL,19,Fprices across the world.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
